START
create a file and class for each page of the ATM
IMPORT java Swing
IMPORT java awt
    Create text labels and input fields  to gather user input for card # and Pin #
    IF card # and Pin # match
        accept an input from the user as to what they would like to do next
        WHILE LOOP user choice != exit
            execute whichever command the user requests
        ELSE
            EXIT
        END LOOP
    ELSE
        OUTPUT 'Pin or Card # invalid. Try again.'
    END IF


END